                <h1>Basset Hounds: The Charming Hunting Dogs</h1>
                <p>Basset Hounds are indeed hunting dogs, originally bred in France for tracking small game like rabbits. Their keen sense of smell and strong tracking instincts make them skilled hunters. While they are friendly and affectionate pets today, their hunting heritage influences their curious and determined nature, making them unique companions.</p>
